</section>
<div data-type="glossary"><h3 data-type="glossary-title">Glossary</h3>
<dl id="fs-idm113628896">
<dt>inert pair effect</dt>
<dd id="fs-idm29656464">tendency of heavy atoms to form ions in which their valence <em data-effect="italics">s</em> electrons are not lost</dd>
</dl>
<dl id="fs-idm118453184">
<dt>ionic bond</dt>
<dd id="fs-idm101179264">strong electrostatic force of attraction between cations and anions in an ionic compound</dd>
</dl>
</div></body>

